ks whether a feminist-friendly future is possible, or indeed, desirable.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aFeminism. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Feminism & Feminist Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z9783111196435oZDB-23-BUPP0 cprintz978144732817940uhttps://doi.org/10.56687/9781447328186?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447328186423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447328186/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-BUPPb2016